nter\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:&quot;color:#000000;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">翟渊鹏</span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width=\"446\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:&quot;color:#000000;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">25.</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">高频超声检查在骨科人工关节置换术后的临床应用价值</span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"109\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:&quot;color:#000000;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">乔雅馨</span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width=\"446\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:&quot;color:#000000;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">26.</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">翻转课堂在超声住院医师规范化培训教学中的应用</span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"109\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:&quot;color:#000000;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">胡文笳</span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td width=\"446\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:&quot;color:#000000;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">27.</span><span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">意大利超声医学学科建设见闻</span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n			<td width=\"109\">\r\n				<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n					<span style=\"font-family:新宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">王</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"color:#000000;font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">华</span></span>\r\n				</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>', '<span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:2;\">一、参会人员</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:2;\">1.各级医院超声医学科及相关科室的临床、医技医生、技术员、护士人员等；</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:2;\">2.河南省医学会超声医学分会第六届委员会委员 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 同志，请务必准时参加10月27日下午17:00-18:00召开的全体委员会会议。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:2;\">3.河南省医学会超声医学分会第二届青年委员会、心血管学组、腹部学组、妇产科学组、介入学组、浅表器官和外周血管学组委员<u>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</u>&nbsp;同志，请务必按时参加学术会议。 &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:2;\">4.请各位委员积极组织本地区有关人员踊跃参加会议，本次会议将公布各位委员所在地区组稿和代表参会情况。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:2;\">5.<u>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</u>&nbsp;同志的论文《 &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;》已被会议录用，请按时参加会议。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:2;\">二、注意事项</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:2;\">1.参会代表交会务费550元，住宿统一安排（按宾馆要求，办理住宿者请携带身份证），费用回单位报销。乡镇医院医生免交会务费、注册费、资料费（必需有乡村医师资格证书及单位证明）。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:2;\">2.此次会议为国家级继续医学教育项目【项目编号：2017-09-02-144 】，会后将授予国家级继续医学教育学分10分。凡不到会者不发学分证，会后不再补发。</span>', '<span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:2;\">会议时间：2017年10月27—29日（27日14：00-20：00在紫荆山宾馆1号楼一楼大厅报到）</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:2;\">会议地点：紫荆山宾馆（郑州市金水区金水路8号，金水路与经三路交叉口西北角）</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:2;\">乘车路线：郑州火车站北出站口乘26路公交车在国际饭店站下车回走300米过丁字路口西北角即到；郑州东站乘坐916路，在国际饭店站下车回走300米过丁字路口西北角即到；</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:2;\">火车站西广场乘坐地铁1号线(市体育中心方向)或郑州东站乘坐地铁1号线(西流湖方向)，在紫荆山站下车(E口出)向东步行1200米路口西北角即到。</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;line-height:2;\">宾馆服务台电话：0371-81676288 &nbsp; 81676388 &nbsp;</span>', '<span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height:2;\">大会秘书处</span></strong><br />\r\n<span style=\"line-height:2;\">河南省医学会</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">李小龙</span><span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;:&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">0371-85963308</span><br />\r\n<span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">15824851311</span></span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">河南省人民医院</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><br />\r\n</span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;background-color:#FFFFFF;\"> \r\n<p>\r\n	<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">吴</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\"><span style=\"line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">刚&nbsp; :&nbsp;</span><span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">18538298205&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:14px;line-height:2;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n</span>', '2018-01-27 20:58:41', '1', '重庆渝北');
